<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="22" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,370,1748]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,351,370,396]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Description.</emphasis>
Male deep-brown with partly mottled light spots and short whitish marking posteriorly on back of prosoma. Female beige with scattered dark streaks.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,370,1748]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis box="[198,267,455,480]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Male.</emphasis>
